column5: Hi guys I need to make a repair this weekend.  where can i get some? any idea on cost?  Thanks  Speed
Locally A&M Wood Specialties in Cambridge. Its not cheap you have to buy full sheets. They are in the phone book give them a call.

Noah's Marine Supply near Bloor and Kipling in Etobicoke.  54 Six Point Rd, Toronto, ON, M8Z 2X2 Phone (416) 232-0522 Fax (800) 894-1783 or (416) 232-0522  Monday to Friday 9:00AM - 5:30PM Saturday 9:00AM - 1:00PM
Hey Rob, I just picked up two sheets of okoume 3/4" marine ply for $126 each. 1/2" is $96 each. They stock it. Ontario Plywood Specialties John 257 Centennial Prky N. Hamilton 905-561-3576
You were just around the corner from me and you didn't drop by?
